schools.name: Paseo Del Rey Natural Science Magnet

data.description: REDUCED PRICE! NEW FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT HOME! Welcome to your seaside sanctuary at 7920 W 79th St, nestled in the highly desirable Playa del Rey neighborhood. This traditional-style family home sits on a tranquil street atop the Playa del Rey hillside. Enjoy the tranquility of residing across the street from a landscaped greenbelt. The home features a large primary bedroom, warm touches of oak molding, a family room with views to its beautiful backyard oasis that features a rock pond, and both a detached double garage and porte cochere. The detached garage is about 400 sq ft and has the potential to be a spacious studio unit or workspace. The home has been well-maintained and cherished through the years by one family and is available for the first time since being built in 1962. Recent updates and maintenance include a new roof in 2023 and tent termite treatment in 2021. This well-loved, one-family home can be easily updated to reflect the colors and styles of the new owner. Enjoy the gentle sea breeze and the best of coastal living being near the beautiful secluded beaches of Playa del Rey, as well as the proximity of LAX being minutes away without the air traffic noise. Stroll to the shoreline or visit the nearby Marina del Rey for dining, shopping, and entertainment and return to your special home in Playa del Rey. Agents see notes.
